# Keep the build context small and deterministic. The images install
# dependencies from the committed lockfile inside the build stage, so nothing
# generated locally should ever be shipped into the context.

# Dependencies & build output (rebuilt in-image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.expo
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# VCS & CI
.git
.github
.husky

# Secrets & local env — never bake into an image layer
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production.example
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*-service-account*.json

# Editor / OS noise
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docs & meta not needed at build time
docs
*.md
!README.md
